{
  "uid": "grob-audit-agent",
  "title": "Grob — Audit agent",
  "tags": ["grob", "audit", "gouvernance", "investigation", "démo"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 2,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "time": { "from": "now-3h", "to": "now" },
  "links": [
    {
      "type": "link",
      "title": "Vue RSSI",
      "url": "/d/grob-rssi-business/grob-decision-rssi-ia?orgId=1",
      "icon": "external link",
      "includeVars": false,
      "keepTime": true,
      "targetBlank": false
    },
    {
      "type": "link",
      "title": "Observabilité technique",
      "url": "/d/grob-overview/grob-otel-metrics-logs-traces?orgId=1",
      "icon": "external link",
      "includeVars": false,
      "keepTime": true,
      "targetBlank": false
    }
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "tenant",
        "label": "Agent / identité",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
        "query": {
          "label": "tenant",
          "stream": "{service=\"grob-audit\"}",
          "type": 1,
          "refId": "LokiVariableQueryEditor-VariableQuery"
        },
        "definition": "label_values({service=\"grob-audit\"}, tenant)",
        "regex": "/^(alice|bob|dev-bot|compta-bot)$/",
        "sort": 1,
        "includeAll": false,
        "multi": false,
        "current": { "text": "alice", "value": "alice" },
        "refresh": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n\n# Investigation agent — $tenant\n\n### Décision, incidents, preuve signée et `trace_id` pour chaque requête de cette identité.\n\n**Classification :** NC = propre · C1 = caviardé · C2 = PII / restreint · C3 = attaque bloquée\n\n</div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Événements signés",
      "description": "Volume d'audit pour $tenant sur la fenêtre. Chaque événement est horodaté, chaîné et signé.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "noValue": "0",
          "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["sum"] },
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"}[$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Blocages DLP",
      "description": "Tentatives bloquées pour $tenant avant sortie : injection, exfiltration ou donnée interdite.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "noValue": "0",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1 }
            ]
          },
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["sum"] },
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json | action=`DLP_BLOCK` [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Décision majoritaire",
      "description": "Action la plus fréquente pour $tenant : réponse autorisée, requête traitée ou blocage DLP.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "string",
          "noValue": "—",
          "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "purple" },
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "DLP_BLOCK": { "text": "Bloqué", "color": "red", "index": 0 } } },
            { "type": "value", "options": { "RESPONSE": { "text": "Réponse", "color": "green", "index": 1 } } },
            { "type": "value", "options": { "REQUEST_PROCESSED": { "text": "Traité", "color": "green", "index": 2 } } }
          ]
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "/^action$/" },
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "textMode": "value",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "topk(1, sum by (action) (count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json [$__range])))",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Preuve d'intégrité",
      "description": "Nombre de lignes signées pour $tenant. Les détails exposent signature, previous_hash, trace_id et span_id.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "noValue": "—",
          "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" },
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "range", "options": { "from": 1, "to": 1000000000, "result": { "text": "Signée", "color": "green", "index": 0 } } },
            { "type": "range", "options": { "from": 0, "to": 0, "result": { "text": "—", "color": "yellow", "index": 1 } } }
          ]
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["sum"] },
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "textMode": "value",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json | signature=~`.+` [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Incidents hors NC",
      "description": "Nombre d'événements non propres pour $tenant : C1, C2 ou C3. 0 signifie aucun incident sur la fenêtre.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "noValue": "0",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 1 }
            ]
          },
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["sum"] },
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json | classification!=`NC` [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "Répartition des classifications — $tenant",
      "description": "Répartition NC/C1/C2/C3 issue du champ `classification` de l'audit signé.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 9, "x": 8, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
        },
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "NC - propre" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "C1 - caviardé" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange" } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "C2 - PII / restreint" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "yellow" } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "C3 - attaque bloquée" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } } ] }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "pieType": "donut",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["sum"], "values": false },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "values": ["value"] },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json | classification=`NC` [$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "NC - propre",
          "queryType": "instant"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json | classification=`C1` [$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "C1 - caviardé",
          "queryType": "instant"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json | classification=`C2` [$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "C2 - PII / restreint",
          "queryType": "instant"
        },
        {
          "refId": "D",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json | classification=`C3` [$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "C3 - attaque bloquée",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Classifications par minute — $tenant",
      "description": "Évolution NC/C1/C2/C3 par minute. Une montée C2/C3 rend la dérive de l'agent visible avant coupure.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 7, "x": 17, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 70,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "A" }
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "NC" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } }, { "id": "displayName", "value": "NC - propre" } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "C1" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange" } }, { "id": "displayName", "value": "C1 - caviardé" } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "C2" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "yellow" } }, { "id": "displayName", "value": "C2 - PII / restreint" } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "C3" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } }, { "id": "displayName", "value": "C3 - attaque bloquée" } ] }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum by (classification) (count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json [1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{classification}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Événements signés par minute — $tenant",
      "description": "Volume de lignes d'audit signées pour $tenant. Sert de base de comparaison pour les incidents et blocages.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 45,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "gradientMode": "opacity"
          },
          "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json | signature=~`.+` [1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Événements signés / min"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Incidents hors NC par minute — $tenant",
      "description": "Événements C1/C2/C3 pour $tenant. La courbe isole ce qui n'est pas du trafic propre.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 50,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "gradientMode": "opacity"
          },
          "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange" }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json | classification!=`NC` [1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Incidents hors NC / min"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Blocages DLP par minute — $tenant",
      "description": "Rythme des blocages DLP de $tenant. Un pic signale une dérive exploitable par le watcher ou une policy de coupure.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 50,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "gradientMode": "opacity"
          },
          "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json | action=`DLP_BLOCK` [1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Violations DLP / min"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Tempo traces — requêtes grob",
      "description": "Liste les spans http_request émis par grob. Les trace_id correspondent aux champs trace_id présents dans le journal Loki signé.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 23 },
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
      "options": { "showHeader": true },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{ resource.service.name = \"grob\" && name = \"http_request\" }",
          "limit": 50
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Corrélation trace_id",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 23 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "1. Ouvrir une ligne du **Journal signé**.\n2. Copier `trace_id`.\n3. Retrouver la même trace dans **Tempo traces** ou Tempo Explore.\n\nChaque requête auditée porte aussi `span_id`, `signature` et `previous_hash`.\n\nLe **service graph** reste vide dans cette démo parce que seul `grob` émet des spans OTel ; le provider mock nginx n'est pas instrumenté."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Journal signé avec trace_id — $tenant",
      "description": "Chaque ligne résume classification, action, règle DLP, signature et trace_id. Déplier la ligne expose le JSON complet et permet la corrélation Tempo.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 14, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 33 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": false,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": false,
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "{service=\"grob-audit\", tenant=\"$tenant\"} | json classification=`classification`, action=`action`, dlp_rule=`dlp_rules_triggered[0]`, signature=`signature`, trace_id=`trace_id` | line_format `[{{.classification}}] {{.action}}{{if .dlp_rule}} · règle DLP: {{.dlp_rule}}{{end}} · sig={{printf \"%.16s\" .signature}}… · trace={{printf \"%.16s\" .trace_id}}…`",
          "queryType": "range"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
